General.Name: V-Tac Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: V-TAC Technology Co.,Ltd. operates as an IC application design house and IC sales agent in Taiwan, Hong Kong, and China. The company designs and offers solution for electronic product in consumer market, including LCD game, universal remote control, calculator, timepiece, sport-meter, and health care products; and telecommunication products, such as caller ID, answering machines, and commercial terminals based on PSTN wired tele-transport technology. It also provides solutions for USB connected storage devices that include card readers, thumb drivers, U-disks, and HUB/IDE/SATA; multi-media products consisting of DPF/MP3/TV entertainment/PMP/media players; and ELA and toy products, including translator, dictionary, RF pen, optical learning aid, kids laptop, and interactive toys. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
General.Address: No. 99, Xintai 5th Road, New Taipei City, Taiwan
